// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1077 — Mass File Rename (akira)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 3edbc4bc-bb77-57cd-9657-997af8799869

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
